{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act16side", "eventName": "吾導先路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GA-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "光與影", "storyInfo": "當一名薩科塔向拉特蘭教宗提問：拉特蘭教為什麼不拯救？他能夠得到的回答是沉默。這是比答案更好的答案。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g11_laterano_alley", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$exciting_intro", "key": "$exciting_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 100.0, "g": 100.0, "b": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔呃......", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了，帕蒂亞。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還......沒......", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你叫帕蒂亞，對嗎？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$2"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大部分銃騎都已經調到使節區了。你的任務已經完成了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#2$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我是不明白啦，安多恩又不是不知道大教堂裡最強的究竟是誰......耍這些花招有什麼意義？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他只是要確保能見到閣下吧。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$2"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？蕾繆安說的那些，你真聽進去了？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$2"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩碼事。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他可以去結清他的帳。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不等於我就會放過他。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題。那走？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$2"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......先把帕蒂亞安置好。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喲。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們該如何面對啟示？那些神秘莫測、不可言說的時刻；那些模棱兩可、亟待闡釋的衝動；那些無法歸因、晦澀難言的直覺......", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它要把我們引向何方？它想讓我們做何選擇？抑或，這不過是生存的疲乏帶來的幻覺？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但啟示被稱為啟示。只因為我們願意相信，或被告知要相信。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至，就算我們明知其中並無任何超脫常理之處，即使我們已能夠將其分解為冰冷的邏輯或客觀的自然......", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可歎的世人們啊，依舊會為“啟示”覆上一層屬靈的光。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如此，當面對現實的殘酷，怯懦者可以責怪啟示的曖昧，虔信者可以愧悔領悟的偏差，無論如何，至少可以篤定一切並非自己所致。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩，你來了。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你似乎並不意外。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會將這稱為某種指引的結果。生活給我的最大教訓就是，人們總會相遇，無論本意為何。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但終歸各懷目的。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至高律法的看守者、監督者、踐行者。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "承襲了擁有犧牲與團結美德的伊萬傑利斯塔之名的第十一世聖徒，立於拉特蘭聖跡頂點的教宗閣下。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何必背誦你不相信的禮辭？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個女孩沒有留在你們之中。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還小，還有許多事要經歷。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們卻已經老了，老到嫺熟於陰謀、權術、挑撥和傾軋。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算怎麼辦，好好對她使用一番這些歲月的禮物嗎？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒有糊塗到去擋一個小女孩的路。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算她引發了某種“奇跡”？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，奇跡屬於拉特蘭，奇跡只屬於拉特蘭。恩典降臨了，僅此而已。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g3_laterano_cathedralballroom", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你喜歡讀歷史嗎？我相當喜歡。歷史要成為歷史，通常需要一個原點，混雜一些變數，再激起陣陣漣漪——那些漣漪就是歷史。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於最初投進水中的是什麼，也許歷史並不在乎。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不在乎。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "名叫塞茜莉亞的女孩會去到她想去的地方，做她想做的事，將來的某天，塞茜莉亞這個名字可能會大放異彩——也可能默默無聞。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這些，與你我無關了。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與你我無關，這是我們的共識，對嗎？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你把自己描述得像是送孫女出門的溫柔爺爺。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了吧，這只是各取所需。你掌握了奇跡的解釋權，以此為代價，塞茜莉亞換得離開這裡的自由。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這甚至不能算是一場交易，她根本沒得選。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我從沒打算對她做些什麼。矗立數千年的拉特蘭不應、不會，也不可能因一個混血兒動搖。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "願你的前任和繼任們也都這麼想，願那些被抹去的名字不是白白消亡。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們無法奢求得太多，安多恩。罪孽永遠都是罪孽。只是時間會將它沖刷得淡漠。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "淡漠到所有人都忘了這曾是罪孽。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法責怪前人的謹慎。不過，我也不會為了掩蓋而把罪孽化為成規。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前提是你口中的那個“共識”，對吧？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，所以說，變老是一件很無聊的事。經歷過的事情讓我們畏首畏尾，瞻前顧後。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人沒有可能性，安多恩。我們只能沿著已有的道路往前走。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已有的道路......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是一樣，安多恩。我知曉你的跋涉。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#10$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跋涉啊......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我曾跋涉......聆聽最純潔的祈禱，也聽聞最惡毒的詛咒。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我踏入豪奢的宮殿，也將靴子從血污中拔出。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見無恥的罪人痛哭請求寬恕，也為無辜的孩子闔上簡陋的棺材。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總是如此。他們的呐喊歸於沉寂，他們的淚水一再乾涸。而我，我總是站在他們身旁，一再試圖安慰。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說得救終會來臨，只要我們遵循，只要我們篤信。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，什麼都沒有發生。連淡淡的一瞥都沒有換來。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從未因風暴而傾頹的聖城拉特蘭，安坐於柔軟扶手椅上的聖賢，以渾噩自大為美德的薩科塔，怎知人世間竟還有一種境遇叫做苦難？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有這些無望的告解，所有這些乾枯的慰藉，所有這些深重的沉默。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知這沉默如何壓在我的心頭？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來尋求一個答案。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們從來不會得救。對嗎？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“得救”，我常聽信徒們說起這個詞，彷彿這是某種冥冥之中的應允，是溺水者能夠棲身的小舟。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看啊，我們偉大的拉特蘭，金碧輝煌，莊嚴典雅，空氣永遠彌漫香草和砂糖的味道。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#6$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切都是遵循律法的“回報”，這一切都是“得救的證明”。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可樂園之所以成為樂園，只因為外面的曠野太過寒冷。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡本可成為荒野上的星辰，寒夜中的炬火！", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......別試圖否認，拉特蘭不是經書上的陳跡，拉特蘭立於此時此地......立於現世！拉特蘭可以救人！", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可以。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憑什麼？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#4$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憑我們是“我們”。憑我們是拉特蘭的薩科塔。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而“他們”不是“我們”。“他們”，他們會隱瞞，會幻滅，會寄託，會失望，會掙扎，會痛恨。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會自己為自己塑造敵人。毀滅的熾焰藏於心中，欲望和羞恥融合為噬人的怪獸。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼這片大地上無數城邦與王國困於戰火，轉瞬即逝，為什麼奇跡的拉特蘭永世長存？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩，他們是地獄。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你，選擇遠離“我們”，遠離構築我們的一切美德，固執地認為杯水能撲滅火獄，殘燭能照亮荒夜。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何需我的答案？你早已為自己選擇絕望。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#3$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我曾三度來到拉特蘭。更多的時候，我遊蕩於這片大地的角落。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾見許多人。人內心幽暗，不須拉特蘭教宗屈尊告知我。然而人心又有光芒，如此耀眼，幾乎使我目盲。我無法忘懷。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法忘懷。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我被那樣的光芒引燃。也許火燃起的一瞬就註定熄滅的一刻，我再無法回歸恒久光明的拉特蘭。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可恒久的光明冰冷且遙遠，拉特蘭的輝煌只為選定之人敞開，拉特蘭的強大只為澆築榮光而煊赫。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我寧願做行將凍斃者腳邊的炬火。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使這炬火轉瞬即逝。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩，炬火註定轉瞬即逝。你要將恒久的光明變成火焰，火焰就會有熄滅的一天。到那時，遙遠的光明都不復存在。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若你打碎天上的雙月，寒夜中的人無可仰望，唯有閉上雙眼，光明終成為幻想與騙局。你果真相信那樣的永夜更有良心？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你痛恨樂園的狹小。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可知在這片大地，即使是如此狹小的樂園，它要存在，何等之難？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你痛恨樂園的狹小，卻是否想過樂園中也有真實生活的眾人。你有何理由把樂園當成你的薪柴，去點燃你那註定熄滅的野火？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片大地似乎難以容忍美善。為了證明美善可以長存，拉特蘭人，無數的拉特蘭人，世世代代的拉特蘭人，付出多少？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩，你又是什麼人，能輕易開口，隻言片語，便否認這一切？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#7$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......荒謬。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭有真實生活的眾人，拉特蘭之外眾人的生活......難道虛假？！", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在困苦中心懷希望，他們虔信教約與法則，他們相信生活可以改變，他們期盼付出能換來回報......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "苦鹽雜貨店的巴倫大嬸，濤聲小教堂的蘭迪輔祭，為戒鐘搓繩子的小薩格雷......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，他們的相信和期盼何錯之有？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，背負歷史的、保護樂園的、偉大的、光榮的伊萬傑利斯塔十一世。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......潮石鎮為什麼只配得毀滅？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "答案。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問題。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來這是我想要的答案。"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來這是我想問的問題。"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunload", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼鬆動了。"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經長久......束縛著我的。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼在嘯叫......掙扎。"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我卻只覺得輕鬆。"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿沐浴在微鹹的陽光裡。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunshot", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i10", "xScale": 1.4, "yScale": 1.4}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i10", "xScale": 1.6, "yScale": 1.6, "y": 300.0, "x": 400.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunsingle", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "槍聲幾乎同時響起。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i10", "xScale": 0.9, "yScale": 0.9}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "律法深深銘刻在薩科塔的骨與血。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僭越必付出代價。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知如此。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腳下有萬丈深淵。"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已邁步。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 100.0, "g": 100.0, "b": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨力將我砸進牆壁，浮雕硌著骨頭，聖像在背後碎裂崩塌。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毫無疑問，那是守護銃的威力。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世，他衰老的軀體比看起來更強大。"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我努力睜開眼睛，在煙塵中尋找他的身影。"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#4$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個老人依然屹立於大教堂中心，只是面上不再有笑容。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他看上去比我踏進此處時又老了一點點。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但光環，他頭上的光環，依舊閃耀——"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“骨血中的律法，慘痛的代價。”"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......代......價......？"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，我發現了真正的問題。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我頭上的光環也沒有黯淡分毫。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......原來如此。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#4$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你我都平安無事，這真是稀奇。不過值得慶賀。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#4$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我已準備好付出代價。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是個虔誠的信徒，安多恩，或許正因為你不生在拉特蘭。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在拉特蘭，我們並不“信仰”，不是嗎？我們生為信仰的一部分。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩科塔，在光環閃耀於頭頂的那一刻，就已經被它囊括其中了。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它......？我們......薩科塔堅信的律法......到底是什麼？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#3$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "墮天......究竟是......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#3$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在拉特蘭的漫長歷史中，每一任教宗都有權力闡釋律法，繼而衍生戒律、規則，乃至構築於其上的一切。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭奠基於律法。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩科塔知悉：違背規則、違背戒律、違背律法，即迎來墮天。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "墮天的薩科塔不再與薩科塔連接，守護銃從此拒斥他。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "墮天的薩科塔不再是薩科塔。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼“是”薩科塔？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩科塔無法對薩科塔舉銃，這是戒律，也是本能。如同人立於懸崖，不願向前邁步。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，總有人能跳下去。這件事你似乎相當有發言權。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#9$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我與她又有何不同？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說戒律是本能。我說戒律是闡釋。以你之穎悟，不該看不出其中齟齬。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......若律法恒定，隨歷史流變加諸其上的“闡釋”不可能成為“本能”。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯。但你想要質疑的前提錯了。律法當然是恒定的......只是“闡釋”並沒有那麼“流變”。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "闡釋不是偶然，安多恩，你能明白嗎？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你剛才說，“老人沒有可能性”。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "律法比你我都要老得更多。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗不闡釋律法，律法闡釋它自己。你覺得律法為什麼能做到這一點？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看我們身邊這些——不好意思，被我打碎了一部分——這些建築、聖像、彩色玻璃、輝煌的穹頂和壁畫......", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們是不是給了我們什麼錯覺？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得“啟示”嗎？", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......即使我們明知其中並無任何超脫常理之處，即使我們已能夠將其分解為冰冷的邏輯或客觀的自然......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可歎的世人們啊，依舊會為它覆上一層屬靈的光。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真正的律法從來就只有一條。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——讓我們的存在延續下去。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“我們”，是什麼？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟隨我。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gateopen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i11", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我跟隨這位老者向深處行進。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "大教堂之下是諸位聖賢埋骨之地，人盡皆知。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他們是拉特蘭漫長歷史中的最淵博者和最傑出者。他們光潔的大理石塑像雙眼空洞，對過路人熟視無睹。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "向下。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "記述歷代教宗偉業的石碑依次陳列。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他們之中有自負者，有謙遜者，有高尚者，或許也有瘋子。但從沒有一位讓拉特蘭蒙塵。如今，他們不發一言。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "向下。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "最古老的聖徒在此長眠。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他們將薩科塔從混沌中引來，他們的身上有著人間的一切美德，所有後來者不過是效仿。鐫刻著他們奇跡的銘牌黯淡無光。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$factory_low_drone", "channel": "bgs", "crossfade": 1.0, "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "向下。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我已經不知身處何方。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "目力所及的一切從未在任何典籍中記述，我無法理解。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這不該屬於拉特蘭。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "低沉的嗡鳴聲充斥整個空間。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我竟然開始感到慌亂......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這不是我想要的答案，這不是人力的創制或附會......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這不會被詮釋、解經、辯論抑或改革所動搖......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這不是信與不信、為何信或如何信的鬥爭......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "因為這是無可辯駁的存在。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它以這樣的方式。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "存在。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "拉特蘭是什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "薩科塔是什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "原來如此。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們之所以是我們，僅僅是因為——", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它將我們連接。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它將我們塑造。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它即為一切的準繩。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你我所行之路，皆為律法所倡。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你我所涉之道，不過殊途同歸。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它允許你我繼續前行。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這正是它判准的道路。", "name": "伊萬傑利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}